{
  "_comment": "Add-ons that TreeCapitator advertises compatibility with (see wiki/treecapitator/compatibility.html). All are watched via chunk.gg, whose product pages are server-rendered: a plain fetch already contains the changelog and an \"updated on <date>\" line (minecraft.net blocks bots; chunk.gg API is auth-only). Per addon: fetch+strip the page, gate change-detection on signal_pattern (the updated-on date), and let the AI read the changelog. marketplace_url only enriches notifications.",
